    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"Peace is found in letting go\"... it sounds so seductive when you put it that way. Like a heavy cloak being lifted from my shoulders. But how does one actually... let go? How does one truly step into that silence and leave the noise of this wretched world behind?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
